msgstr "kísérteties módon visszatükrözi a csillagok és a hold fényét"

#. NIGHTMARES={add="it reminds those that look upon it of their most
#. unpleasant
#. memories"}
#: data/vanilla/vanilla_procedural/scripts/generators/creatures.lua:1874
